description:
Welcome to my course on "Statistics Concepts - Hypothesis Testing Step by Step"

This course will cover the complete understanding of Hypothesis Testing in Statistics . In this course students will learn the numerically and theoratically concepts of Hypothesis Testing. And also they can download material in the form of PDF Files .

With a lot of Examples that will clear the concepts of Hypothesis Testing , and they will learn how to solve the questions of Hypothesis Testing. So

We Will Cover

  • Understand the Basic concepts of Hypothesis Testing
  • What is Hypothesis? and its Basics
  • Simple , Composite and types of Error (Type I Error and Type II Error) etc etc
  • And many more basic and advance concepts of Hypothesis Testing
title: Learn Hypothesis Testing Step by Step ( A Complete Course )
